{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"toolu_vrtx_01951jt921gkGPYrUtZ2V3Dn","content":"[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"{\\\"issues\\\":[{\\\"id\\\":\\\"JEM-89\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"State file for thread links and workspace history\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Add `src/state.rs` to read/write `~/.config/ishi/state.toml`. Two data structures:\\\\n\\\\n* **Thread links**: maps thread ID → issue identifier + workspace path. One issue can have many threads, but each thread belongs to exactly one issue.\\\\n* **Workspace history**: ordered list of previously used directory paths, most recent first. Used by the workspace picker when starting new threads.\\\\n\\\\nFunctions: `load()`, `save()`, `add_thread_link()`, `threads_for… (truncated, use `get_issue` for full description)\\\",\\\"projectMilestone\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"d2f17c9a-0039-4861-a5db-b44495d5ec6b\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Phase 5: Amp Integration\\\"},\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://linear.app/squareup/issue/JEM-89\\\",\\\"gitBranchName\\\":\\\"jmawson/jem-89-state-file-for-thread-links-and-workspace-history\\\",\\\"createdAt\\\":\\\"2026-03-18T04:51:07.087Z\\\",\\\"updatedAt\\\":\\\"2026-03-18T04:51:50.136Z\\\",\\\"archivedAt\\\":null,\\\"completedAt\\\":null,\\\"dueDate\\\":null,\\\"slaStartedAt\\\":null,\\\"slaMediumRiskAt\\\":null,\\\"slaHighRiskAt\\\":null,\\\"slaBreachesAt\\\":null,\\\"slaType\\\":\\\"all\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"Backlog\\\",\\\"labels\\\":[],\\\"createdBy\\\":\\\"Jeremy Mawson\\\",\\\"createdById\\\":\\\"f265a57f-26ba-4ba6-a014-a1414e9067c4\\\",\\\"assignee\\\":\\\"Jeremy Mawson\\\",\\\"assigneeId\\\":\\\"f265a57f-26ba-4ba6-a014-a1414e9067c4\\\",\\\"project\\\":\\\"ishi\\\",\\\"projectId\\\":\\\"032af957-d258-43a4-9cac-246a45582daa\\\",\\\"team\\\":\\\"Jem\\\",\\\"teamId\\\":\\\"3dddde93-b00c-4573-a596-2475a0f69d3a\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"JEM-90\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Amp thread reader — parse thread metadata from JSON files\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Add `src/amp.rs` to scan `~/.local/share/amp/threads/*.json` and parse minimal metadata for each thread:\\\\n\\\\n* `id` (thread ID)\\\\n* `title`\\\\n* `created` (timestamp)\\\\n* message count (`messages.len()`)\\\\n* last message timestamp (derived from messages or file mtime)\\\\n\\\\nProvide `fn read_thread(id) -> Thread` and `fn list_threads() -> Vec<Thread>`. Only parse what we need — don't load full message content.\\\\n\\\\nUnit tests with fixture JSON files.\\\",\\\"projectMilestone\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"d2f17c9a-0039-4861-a5db-b44495d5ec6b\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Phase 5: Amp Integration\\\"},\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://linear.app/squareup/issue/JEM-90\\\",\\\"gitBranchName\\\":\\\"jmawson/jem-90-amp-thread-reader-parse-thread-metadata-from-json-files\\\",\\\"createdAt\\\":\\\"2026-03-18T04:51:10.790Z\\\",\\\"updatedAt\\\":\\\"2026-03-18T04:51:44.781Z\\\",\\\"archivedAt\\\":null,\\\"completedAt\\\":null,\\\"dueDate\\\":null,\\\"slaStartedAt\\\":null,\\\"slaMediumRiskAt\\\":null,\\\"slaHighRiskAt\\\":null,\\\"slaBreachesAt\\\":null,\\\"slaType\\\":\\\"all\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"Backlog\\\",\\\"labels\\\":[],\\\"createdBy\\\":\\\"Jeremy Mawson\\\",\\\"createdById\\\":\\\"f265a57f-26ba-4ba6-a014-a1414e9067c4\\\",\\\"assignee\\\":\\\"Jeremy Mawson\\\",\\\"assigneeId\\\":\\\"f265a57f-26ba-4ba6-a014-a1414e9067c4\\\",\\\"project\\\":\\\"ishi\\\",\\\"projectId\\\":\\\"032af957-d258-43a4-9cac-246a45582daa\\\",\\\"team\\\":\\\"Jem\\\",\\\"teamId\\\":\\\"3dddde93-b00c-4573-a596-2475a0f69d3a\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"JEM-94\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"New thread flow — start Amp session linked to an issue\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Wire `a` key in issue detail view to start a new Amp thread:\\\\n\\\\n1. Show workspace picker → user selects a directory\\\\n2. Snapshot thread IDs from `~/.local/share/amp/threads/`\\\\n3. Suspend ishi\\\\n4. Run `amp threads new` in the chosen directory\\\\n5. On resume, diff thread IDs to detect the newly created thread\\\\n6. If a new thread is found, save thread link (thread_id → issue_id + workspace) to state file\\\\n7. If no new thread detected (user exited without cr… (truncated, use `get_issue` for full description)\\\",\\\"projectMilestone\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"d2f17c9a-0039-4861-a5db-b44495d5ec6b\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Phase 5: Amp Integration\\\"},\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://linear.app/squareup/issue/JEM-94\\\",\\\"gitBranchName\\\":\\\"jmawson/jem-94-new-thread-flow-start-amp-session-linked-to-an-issue\\\",\\\"createdAt\\\":\\\"2026-03-18T04:51:28.424Z\\\",\\\"updatedAt\\\":\\\"2026-03-18T04:51:44.781Z\\\",\\\"archivedAt\\\":null,\\\"completedAt\\\":null,\\\"dueDate\\\":null,\\\"slaStartedAt\\\":null,\\\"slaMediumRiskAt\\\":null,\\\"slaHighRiskAt\\\":null,\\\"slaBreachesAt\\\":null,\\\"slaType\\\":\\\"all\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"Backlog\\\",\\\"labels\\\":[],\\\"createdBy\\\":\\\"Jeremy Mawson\\\",\\\"createdById\\\":\\\"f265a57f-26ba-4ba6-a014-a1414e9067c4\\\",\\\"assignee\\\":\\\"Jeremy Mawson\\\",\\\"assigneeId\\\":\\\"f265a57f-26ba-4ba6-a014-a1414e9067c4\\\",\\\"project\\\":\\\"ishi\\\",\\\"projectId\\\":\\\"032af957-d258-43a4-9cac-246a45582daa\\\",\\\"team\\\":\\\"Jem\\\",\\\"teamId\\\":\\\"3dddde93-b00c-4573-a596-2475a0f69d3a\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"JEM-92\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Workspace picker modal for starting new Amp threads\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"When starting a new Amp thread from the issue detail view, show a workspace picker overlay:\\\\n\\\\n* Lists previously used workspaces from state file, navigable with j/k\\\\n* `/` to type a new path (with Enter to confirm, Esc to cancel)\\\\n* `Enter` on a listed workspace selects it\\\\n* Selected/entered path is saved to workspace history (moved to top if already present)\\\\n\\\\nRenders as a centered popup over the detail view.\\\",\\\"projectMilestone\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"d2f17c9a-0039-4861-a5db-b44495d5ec6b\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Phase 5: Amp Integration\\\"},\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://linear.app/squareup/issue/JEM-92\\\",\\\"gitBranchName\\\":\\\"jmawson/jem-92-workspace-picker-modal-for-starting-new-amp-threads\\\",\\\"createdAt\\\":\\\"2026-03-18T04:51:19.120Z\\\",\\\"updatedAt\\\":\\\"2026-03-18T04:51:44.747Z\\\",\\\"archivedAt\\\":null,\\\"completedAt\\\":null,\\\"dueDate\\\":null,\\\"slaStartedAt\\\":null,\\\"slaMediumRiskAt\\\":null,\\\"slaHighRiskAt\\\":null,\\\"slaBreachesAt\\\":null,\\\"slaType\\\":\\\"all\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"Backlog\\\",\\\"labels\\\":[],\\\"createdBy\\\":\\\"Jeremy Mawson\\\",\\\"createdById\\\":\\\"f265a57f-26ba-4ba6-a014-a1414e9067c4\\\",\\\"assignee\\\":\\\"Jeremy Mawson\\\",\\\"assigneeId\\\":\\\"f265a57f-26ba-4ba6-a014-a1414e9067c4\\\",\\\"project\\\":\\\"ishi\\\",\\\"projectId\\\":\\\"032af957-d258-43a4-9cac-246a45582daa\\\",\\\"team\\\":\\\"Jem\\\",\\\"teamId\\\":\\\"3dddde93-b00c-4573-a596-2475a0f69d3a\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"JEM-86\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Open Linear (o+l) — open selected issue in Linear\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Add a prefix-key action `o` (open) with mnemonic `l` (linear) that opens the Linear app or web page for the currently selected issue. Follows the existing awaiting-mode pattern (like `o` for order-by, `f` for filter-by).\\\",\\\"projectMilestone\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"86c0bff7-a891-44ae-8f63-045f02459b26\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Phase 2: My Issues View\\\"},\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://linear.app/squareup/issue/JEM-86\\\",\\\"gitBranchName\\\":\\\"jmawson/jem-86-open-linear-ol-open-selected-issue-in-linear\\\",\\\"createdAt\\\":\\\"2026-03-18T03:56:11.940Z\\\",\\\"updatedAt\\\":\\\"2026-03-18T03:57:17.579Z\\\",\\\"archivedAt\\\":null,\\\"completedAt\\\":null,\\\"dueDate\\\":null,\\\"slaStartedAt\\\":null,\\\"slaMediumRiskAt\\\":null,\\\"slaHighRiskAt\\\":null,\\\"slaBreachesAt\\\":null,\\\"slaType\\\":\\\"all\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"Backlog\\\",\\\"labels\\\":[],\\\"createdBy\\\":\\\"Jeremy Mawson\\\",\\\"createdById\\\":\\\"f265a57f-26ba-4ba6-a014-a1414e9067c4\\\",\\\"assignee\\\":\\\"Jeremy Mawson\\\",\\\"assigneeId\\\":\\\"f265a57f-26ba-4ba6-a014-a1414e9067c4\\\",\\\"proj